# Generated QA artifacts at the qa/ root.
#
# Every test run `capture erase`s and then regenerates these via export()/
# saving()/save targets, so tracking them produced only binary churn and
# violated the "artifacts never tracked" distribution standard. They are
# recreated on demand by `do run_all.do`, so nothing depends on a tracked copy.
#
# Anchored to the qa/ root with a leading slash so that deliberate INPUT
# fixtures placed under qa/data/ (the repo convention) stay tracked.
/*.dta
/*.xlsx
/*.csv
/*.log
/*.smcl
